docs.text:

docs.text:
There're many commands of uel. Let's learn it.

For example. 

uel run <filename>

docs.title: The all of commands.
docs.text:
This is UEL's commands. This is very simple.

Command name Information run execute UEL source code file.

docs.title: Install by python-pip
docs.text:
If you are a user, It's very simple. use the pip 

pip install uel

docs.title: Install from sources
docs.text:
make
If you cached binary of UEL's extensions, You can using 
make install
